                    </div>
                    <span>Out of all the books in my collection on pediatric cardiac conditions I will have to say that this is the best one out there so far.  It has more defects in it and describes them in simple terms then the others books I have seen.  This is the first book a new parent should purchase when they find out that their child has a cardiac condition.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A must for parents of children with CHD</div>
