                    </div>
                    <span>This book was very informative, but we have found that the newer publication released in 1998 was more up to date. "Heart Defects in Children - What Every Parent Should Know" was written by a nurse, and  has easier to understand explainations of the defects.  It also has a draw  in heart section where you can more easily visualize your child's defect.   Check it out.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Very Good</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
