                    </div>
                    <span>I learned a lot from reading this book when my daughter was in the hospital having her first heart surgery.  But the mortality statistics are outdated.  The outcomes for children having heart surgery and children with HLHS and Truncus are much more hopeful than they were in 1992.</span>
                  
              
